<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;">Dear Mr/Ms {!Opportunity.Name__c},</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><br>
Thank you for your interest in SunPower solar panels.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">We understand that it is
important for you to make the right choice in terms of energy and we are
convinced that our photovoltaic panels, the most reliable and the most
efficient of the panels available on the market, will meet your needs.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">In order to help you
with your project and provide a high level of service, SunPower has developed a
network of local Partners installers, carefully selected and trained in our
technologies.&nbsp; We are very happy to be
able to put you in touch with your local Partner, <b>{!Opportunity.Partner_Account_text__c}<br>
<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br>
<!--[endif]--></b><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Partner Facts: Firmly
established in your area, this Partner has been selected for their
professionalism, a high quality of service and expertise in solar energy. We
are sure that our Partner will be able to help you to navigate your solar
journey and assist you with your project.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">IMPORTANT POINTS<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">• Meet our Partner<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Our local Partner <b>{!Opportunity.Partner_Account_text__c} </b>will
contact you soon within the next 24 hours in order to analyze your needs and
then present to you suitable SunPower solar solutions. The company’s <b>{!Opportunity.Partner_Account_text__c}
</b>representative will also be able to answer any questions you might
have&nbsp; concerning your future photovoltaic
project.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">• Choose a well established company<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">You should be able to choose a
sustainable provider.&nbsp; As an affiliate of
Total, SunPower has been one of the leaders in the solar market for over 25
years.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">• Choose performance and reliability<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Independent tests have proven
that SunPower panels are the most efficient on the market. &nbsp;Our panels not only have an exceptional power,
but also a life cycle exceeding 40 years.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">• Choose local<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Apart from our network
of local Partners, SunPower has several manufacturing facilities in Europe.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p>

